Meyer Burger Reports First-Half Net Solar Sales of $731 Million

-- B y   E l e n a   L o g u t e n k o v a
-- 
2011-08-19T15:54:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-19/meyer-burger-reports-first-half-net-solar-sales-of-731-million.html
Meyer Burger Technology AG (MBTN)  said net
sales reached 575 million Swiss francs in the first half of this
year.  The company is on track to reach the full-year sales target
of 1.2 billion francs, it said in an e-mailed statement today. A
complete earnings report for the first six months of this year
will be published on Sept. 1, it added.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Elena Logutenkova at 
 elogutenkova@bloomberg.net  